_aChangeLog.text: Tweaked the lighting in spawn, redid the 3rd stage a little bit, also made the "big leap" an actual big leap. If anything is wrong let me know!
I fixed the light in spawn which was triggering me, redid the 4th stage, and spruced up the 5th and 6th stages a bit. If anything is wrong let me know!

_sText: This really didn't take me a month to make, I was preoccupied with another game and it took me a while to get away from it to start mapping again. This is no where near completed, I'll update the map with general improvements and perhaps additions, not 100% sure yet. Have fun with this map and let me know if there's anything wrong or there is something I could improve upon.
